                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4913" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">EPSM-0423</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8409 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无障碍艺途：从改变认知到价值创造</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">WABC: From Cognitive Change to Value Creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐京悦，王建英，刘晓梅，李晓光，李东贤</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国人民大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海艺途无障碍工作室</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">24 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">无障碍艺途；精智障人群；社会融合；价值认知；价值创造；2020百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">WABC, Mentally Handicapped, Social Integration, Cognitive Change, Value Creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">成立于2010年的无障碍艺途是一家专门服务于精智障人群的社会企业，为精智障人群提供免费艺术类课程，培养和开发他们艺术潜能，同时也对其进行心理和精神方面的疗愈。为了改变社会公众对精智障群体的认知，无障碍艺途以项目运作的方式举办画展、开展主题活动，并进行线上+线下的宣传。为了有足够的资金支撑组织的持续发展，无障碍艺途逐渐发展出较强的项目筹资能力，并尝试探索自我造血机制。本案例回顾了无障碍艺途创业的历程，并重点介绍了其在开设艺术疗愈课程、改变社会认知以及项目资金筹集方面的创新实践。通过案例学习，学员能够理解社会企业的内涵、了解社会企业商业模式的独特性，感受创始人的社会情怀和企业家精神，也能够站在创始人的角度思考机构面临的挑战及未来的发展方向。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">WABC is a non-governmental public welfare organization, which was officially registered in Shanghai in 2010. As an institution dedicated to the mentally handicapped, WABC provides free art courses for the mentally handicapped to cultivate and develop their artistic potentials, and at the same time to heal them psychologically and spiritually. In order to change the public&#39;s perception of this group, WABC　organizes exhibitions, thematic activities and Online + offline marketing activities. In order to have sufficient funds to support the sustainable development of the organization, WABC has gradually developed a strong project financing capacity, and tried to explore self-hematopoietic mechanism. This case reviews the entrepreneurial process of  WABC, and focuses on its innovative practice in offering art healing courses, changing social awareness and raising project funds. Through case study, students can understand the connotation of social enterprises, the unique business model of social enterprises, understand the founder’s social compassion and entrepreneurship , and　face the challenges in future development  from the perspective of the founder.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《创业管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会创业动机与外部环境因素 企业社会创业内部组织条件 企业社会创业机会开发 共享价值创造与双元价值导向理论 社会创业可持续性发展路径</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-11</td>
                            </tr>
